#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:2
msgid "RESP (Redis/Valkey)"
msgstr "RESP (Redis/Valkey)"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:4
msgid ""
"An L2 adapter backed by a native RESP (Redis Serialization Protocol) "
"connector, targeting **Redis** or **Valkey** servers. I/O is dispatched "
"through a C++ worker-thread pool."
msgstr "由原生 RESP（Redis 序列化协议）连接器驱动的 L2 适配器，面向 **Redis** 或 **Valkey** 服务器。I/O 通过 C++ 工作线程池进行调度。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:8
msgid "**Required fields:**"
msgstr "**必填字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:10
msgid "``host``: Redis/Valkey server hostname or IP."
msgstr "``host``: Redis/Valkey 服务器主机名或 IP。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:11
msgid "``port``: Server port (positive integer)."
msgstr "``port``: 服务器端口（正整数）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:13
msgid "**Optional fields:**"
msgstr "**可选字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:15
msgid "``num_workers`` (int, default ``8``): C++ worker threads for I/O (> 0)."
msgstr "``num_workers`` (int, 默认 ``8``): 用于 I/O 的 C++ 工作线程 (> 0)。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:16
msgid "``username`` (string, default ``\"\"``): Auth username."
msgstr "``username`` (字符串，默认 ``\"\"``)：认证用户名。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:17
msgid "``password`` (string, default ``\"\"``): Auth password."
msgstr "``password`` (字符串，默认 ``\"\"``)：认证密码。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:18
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0``): Max L2 capacity in GB for "
"usage tracking / aggregate eviction. ``0`` disables tracking."
msgstr "``max_capacity_gb`` (float，默认 ``0``)：L2 存储的最大容量上限（GB），用于容量跟踪与聚合逐出。设为 ``0`` 则禁用跟踪。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:21
msgid ""
"When ``host``, ``port``, ``username``, or ``password`` are left empty, "
"the adapter falls back to the corresponding environment variables at "
"creation time: ``LMCACHE_RESP_HOST``, ``LMCACHE_RESP_PORT``, "
"``LMCACHE_RESP_USERNAME``, ``LMCACHE_RESP_PASSWORD``."
msgstr "当 ``host``、``port``、``username`` 或 ``password`` 留空时，适配器在创建时会回退到相应的环境变量： ``LMCACHE_RESP_HOST``、``LMCACHE_RESP_PORT``、``LMCACHE_RESP_USERNAME``、``LMCACHE_RESP_PASSWORD``。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/resp.rst:26
msgid "**Configuration examples:**"
msgstr "**配置示例：**"

